# NRR CX Diagnostics Starter

This repo generates three types of CX diagnostic products for McKinsey client engagements. Each produces a deployable Vercel web app.

## Products

1. **NRR CX Basic** — NRR benchmark + customer journey map + diagnostic synthesis (~2-4 hrs)
2. **NRR CX Enhanced** — Full deep-dive with maturity assessment, waterfall, value-at-stake, and actions (~1-2 days)
3. **Agentic CX Teardown** — How agentic AI transforms CS/PS/Support for a company (~1-2 days)

## Gold Standard Examples

- Basic: https://nrr-cx-okta.vercel.app/
- Enhanced: https://nrr-cx-databricks-enhanced.vercel.app/
- Agentic: https://n-eight-zeta.vercel.app/

## How to Generate

Tell Cursor one of:
- "Generate an NRR CX basic for [Company]"
- "Generate an NRR CX enhanced for [Company]"
- "Generate an agentic CX teardown for [Company]"

Cursor will follow the rules in `.cursor/rules/` for the chosen product type.

## Naming Convention

- `nrr-cx-{client}-basic` or `nrr-cx-{client}-enhanced` for NRR diagnostics
- `agentic-cx-{client}` for agentic teardowns
- Client names: lowercase, hyphens OK (e.g., `databricks`, `t-mobile`)

## Templates

- `templates/basic/` — Next.js template for Basic product
- `templates/enhanced/` — Next.js template + Python scrapers for Enhanced product
- `templates/agentic/` — Next.js template for Agentic Teardown

## After Generation

1. Review the output for accuracy
2. Deploy: `cd output/nrr-cx-{client}-{product} && npx vercel --prod`
3. Update `diagnostics.json` with the new entry

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 16 + React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS 4
- Recharts for charts
- Static export (`output: "export"`) for Vercel deployment
- Python 3.11+ for Enhanced scrapers/analysis (OpenAI API, Reddit API, yfinance)

## Key Rules

- All client-specific content lives in `public/data/client-data.json` — the dashboard reads from this single file
- Never hardcode client names in component code
- Follow the quality checklist before deploying (see `.cursor/rules/`)
- Real verbatim quotes only — never generate fake customer quotes
